<Content><a href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B000UV4EU6/ref=cm_cr_asin_lnk/103-3649011-1477462">Creative Zen 4 GB (Black)</a>  I believe this is the first edition and that later versions may have been perfected.  (I find out know.)  It's good to use for the gym.  I like the fact that I can delete a song directly from the player. (My son's iPod cannot do this.) However, it has stopped working several times and had to be reset.  This is an inconvenience to say the least. The clock doesn't keep correct time.  I don't plan my day by it so I can live with that. Over all it's a great deal for the price. Beats a bulky CD player and more versatile than an armband radio.  
